definitions.definition: A member of an ancient Anatolian people related to the Hittites .

main_definition: A member of an ancient Anatolian people related to the Hittites .

definitions.definition: an extinct language of the Anatolian branch of the Indo-European language family , spoken in the 2nd millennium BC and recorded in both hieroglyphic and cuneiform scripts.

main_definition: an extinct language of the Anatolian branch of the Indo-European language family , spoken in the 2nd millennium BC and recorded in both hieroglyphic and cuneiform scripts.
